         <div type="translation">
            <ab>... having become secretary of finance... and we are happy with your excellent manner, for benevolence towards you and good people like you, and virtue, has been important to us beyond all else.  Be well, master.  From Anoubion, son of Julius, who has become the secretary of finance.</ab>
